commit.message:
objc-act.c (objc_comptypes): Treat comparisons between 'Class' and '<class> *' as explicitly invalid.

[gcc/ChangeLog]
2004-03-24  Ziemowit Laski  <zlaski@apple.com>

        * objc/objc-act.c (objc_comptypes): Treat comparisons
